Package: kcorebip
Title: Bipartite networks kcore decomposition and visualization
Version: 0.9.1
Date: 2023-07-12
Author: Javier Garcia-Algarra [aut, cre], Juan Manuel Garcia Santi [ctb]
Maintainer: Javier Garcia-Algarra <jgalgarra@coit.es>
Description: Functions for k-core decomposing a bipartite graph and visualizing it with two original kind of plots, polar and ziggurat. This package is specially suited for ecological networks.
Depends: ggplot2, rlang, grid, gridExtra, igraph, bipartite, R (>= 3.4)
License: See LICENSE file
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
